<section class="sec" id="demo">
  <div class="wrap split">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow" data-en="Tanzania's only · real-time profit" data-sw="Pekee Tanzania · faida ya papo hapo">Tanzania's only · real-time profit</span>
      <h2 data-en="See real profit, not just sales." data-sw="Ona faida halisi, si mauzo tu.">See real profit, not just sales.</h2>
      <p
        class="lead"
        data-en='Every sale shows your true net profit — automatically calculated after cost of goods, expenses and VAT. No spreadsheets, no month-end surprises. <span class="sw">Faida yako, wakati huu huu.</span>'
        data-sw='Kila mauzo yanaonyesha faida halisi — yanakokotolewa moja kwa moja baada ya gharama, matumizi na VAT. Hakuna lahajedwali, hakuna mshangao wa mwisho wa mwezi. <span class="sw">Faida yako, wakati huu huu.</span>'
      >Every sale shows your true net profit — automatically calculated after cost of goods, expenses and VAT. No spreadsheets, no month-end surprises. <span class="sw">Faida yako, wakati huu huu.</span></p>
      <div class="flist">
        <div class="fl">
          <span class="fc">✓</span>
          <div data-en="<b>After COGS</b> — cost of every item subtracted in real time." data-sw="<b>Baada ya gharama</b> — gharama ya kila bidhaa inakatwa wakati huo huo."><b>After COGS</b> — cost of every item subtracted in real time.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="fl">
          <span class="fc">✓</span>
          <div data-en="<b>After expenses &amp; VAT</b> — what you actually keep, per sale and per day." data-sw="<b>Baada ya matumizi &amp; VAT</b> — kile unachoweka kweli, kwa kila mauzo na kwa siku."><b>After expenses &amp; VAT</b> — what you actually keep, per sale and per day.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="fl">
          <span class="fc">✓</span>
          <div data-en="<b>One-tap reports</b> — daily, weekly and TRA audit PDFs." data-sw="<b>Ripoti kwa mguso mmoja</b> — za kila siku, kila wiki na ukaguzi wa TRA PDF."><b>One-tap reports</b> — daily, weekly and TRA audit PDFs.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="spot-visual reveal">
      <div class="lbl muted" style="font-weight:700;font-size:13px;" data-en="Net profit · today" data-sw="Faida halisi · leo">Net profit · today</div>
      <div class="big">TZS 312,400</div>
      <div class="muted" style="font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600;" data-en="▲ 18% vs yesterday · after COGS, expenses & VAT" data-sw="▲ 18% ikilinganishwa na jana · baada ya gharama, matumizi &amp; VAT">▲ 18% vs yesterday · after COGS, expenses &amp; VAT</div>
      <div class="bars">
        <div class="col"><div class="bar" style="height:42%"></div><span class="bl">Mon</span></div>
        <div class="col"><div class="bar" style="height:58%"></div><span class="bl">Tue</span></div>
        <div class="col"><div class="bar" style="height:50%"></div><span class="bl">Wed</span></div>
        <div class="col"><div class="bar" style="height:72%"></div><span class="bl">Thu</span></div>
        <div class="col"><div class="bar" style="height:64%"></div><span class="bl">Fri</span></div>
        <div class="col"><div class="bar hi" style="height:95%"></div><span class="bl">Sat</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
